message.content:
Certainly! Here's a healthy meal plan for you:

Breakfast: Greek yogurt with mixed berries, chia seeds, and a drizzle of honey. Serve with whole grain toast and a boiled egg on the side.

Snack: Apple slices with almond butter.

Lunch: Grilled chicken breast with brown rice, roasted vegetables (such as broccoli, bell peppers, and mushrooms), and a side salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and balsamic vinaigrette dressing.

Snack: Greek yogurt with sliced banana and a sprinkle of granola.

Dinner: Grilled salmon with quinoa, sautéed spinach, and roasted sweet potatoes. Serve with steamed green beans on the side.

Remember to drink plenty of water throughout the day!
